HENRY: Who is it?
KAREN: It's Belle. Open up.

1805
01:41:53.028 --> 01:41:54.939
BELLE: <i>It's Belle. Let me in.</i>

1806
01:41:55.108 --> 01:41:58.783
Morris didn't come home. He's missing.
I know something's happened.

1807
01:41:58.908 --> 01:42:00.261
