1815
01:42:21.628 --> 01:42:24.586
HENRY: What'll I tell Belle?
JIMMY: Who gives a fuck?

1816
01:42:25.028 --> 01:42:28.020
Tell her he ran off with some broad.
What do you care?

1817
01:42:28.548 --> 01:42:30.584
- Watch this.
- Don't fuck with them.

1818
01:42:30.788 --> 01:42:32.585
JIMMY: I'll bust their fucking balls.

1819
01:42:32.668 --> 01:42:35.546
HENRY: Don't give them the satisfaction.
the fucks.

1820
01:42:36.508 --> 01:42:37.702
[Knocking]

1821
01:42:37.788 --> 01:42:40.063
JIMMY: Come on. fuckos.
Let's go for a ride.

1822
01:42:40.148 --> 01:42:41.263
