<i>some Christmas money.</i>

1830
01:43:53.468 --> 01:43:55.538
<i>From then on. I kept my mouth shut.</i>

1831
01:43:55.948 --> 01:43:58.781
<i>I knew Jimmy. He had the cash.</i>
<i>It was his.</i>

1832
01:43:59.788 --> 01:44:02.939
<i>He kicked some money upstairs to Paulie.</i>
<i>but that was it.</i>

1833
01:44:04.028 --> 01:44:07.384
<i>It made him sick to turn the money over</i>
<i>to the guys who stole it.</i>

1834
01:44:07.468 --> 01:44:10.187
<i>He'd rather whack them. What did I care?</i>

1835
01:44:10.468 --> 01:44:12.504
<i>I wasn't asking for anything.</i>

1836
01:44:12.748 --> 01:44:16.024
<i>And Jimmy was making nice money</i>
<i>through my Pittsburgh connections.</i>

1837
01:44:16.108 --> 01:44:20.181
<i>Still. months after the robbery</i>
<i>they were finding bodies all over.</i>

1838
01:44:21.868 --> 01:44:24.098
[Melody continues. background]

1839
