<i>to thaw him out for the autopsy.</i>

1841
01:44:53.468 --> 01:44:55.698
<i>Still. I never saw Jimmy so happy.</i>

1842
01:44:55.948 --> 01:44:59.224
<i>He was like a kid. We had money</i>
<i>coming in through Pittsburgh...</i>

1843
01:44:59.308 --> 01:45:02.903
<i>... and even after a while.</i>
<i>the Lufthansa thing began to calm down.</i>

1844
01:45:03.068 --> 01:45:05.138
<i>Jimmy was so happy that morning...</i>

1845
01:45:05.308 --> 01:45:08.186
<i>... because this was the day</i>
<i>Tommy was being made.</i>

1846
01:45:08.508 --> 01:45:11.784
<i>Jimmy was so excited.</i>
<i>you'd think he was being made.</i>

1847
01:45:12.028 --> 01:45:14.667
<i>He must have made four calls</i>
<i>to Tommy's house.</i>

1848
01:45:14.908 --> 01:45:18.742
