1852
01:45:27.388 --> 01:45:30.539
You look wonderful. Be careful.
Congratulations.

1853
01:45:31.468 --> 01:45:34.540
I love you. Don't paint
any more religious pictures. please.

1854
01:45:34.628 --> 01:45:35.947
MOTHER: God be with you.

1855
01:45:36.028 --> 01:45:38.667
HENRY: <i>We always called each other</i>
<i>goodfellas.</i>

1856
01:45:38.908 --> 01:45:40.500
<i>You'd say to somebody:</i>

1857
01:45:40.708 --> 01:45:44.747
<i>"You'll like this guy. He's all right.</i>
<i>He's a goodfella. one of us. "</i>

1858
01:45:45.028 --> 01:45:46.347
<i>You understand?</i>

1859
01:45:46.948 --> 01:45:49.064
<i>We were goodfellas. Wiseguys.</i>

1860
01:45:51.628 --> 01:45:54.825
<i>But Jimmy and I could never be made</i>
<i>because we had Irish blood.</i>

1861
01:45:54.908 --> 01:45:57.297
<i>It didn't matter my mother was Sicilian.</i>

1862
01:45:57.508 --> 01:46:01.296
<i>To become a member of a crew</i>
