1894
01:48:23.908 --> 01:48:27.059
<i>It was among the Italians.</i>
<i>It was real greaseball shit.</i>

1895
01:48:28.428 --> 01:48:29.827
[Jimmy sobs]

1896
01:48:39.388 --> 01:48:41.583
HENRY: <i>They even shot Tommy</i>
<i>in the face...</i>

1897
01:48:41.668 --> 01:48:45.183
